Part of the preparatory, conceptual work leading to development of the tool published in this repository was conducted within the project PAM3D. 

The PAM3D project was supported by funds of the Federal Ministry of Food and Agriculture (BMEL) based on a decision of the Parliament of the Federal Republic of Germany via the Federal Office for Agriculture and Food (BLE) under the innovation support programme.

The tool is used as a component of the infrastructures developed for the PAM-M and HortiSem projects, among others.  

The HortiSem project is supported by funds of the Federal Ministry of Food and Agriculture (BMEL) based on a decision of the Parliament of the Federal Republic of Germany via the Federal Office for Agriculture and Food (BLE) under the innovation support programme.

The PAM-M project is supported by funds of the German Government's Special Purpose Fund held at Landwirtschaftliche Rentenbank.